{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"2765c4f4-0f93-4650-a5f5-52dcb082eab5","agentId":"acffc8e30a7e77f77","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"I need you to create a dashboard HTML file for a trading bot called Stockio. The file goes at:\n`d:\\Nextcloud\\Projects\\Stockio\\src\\stockio\\templates\\dashboard.html`\n\nThis is a Flask Jinja2 template served at `/`. It's a single-page dark-mode dashboard that auto-refreshes data from API endpoints.\n\n## Design Requirements\n- Dark mode (dark background, light text, similar to the old version which used #1a1a2e background)\n- Responsive layout\n- Chart.js for P&L chart\n- No external CSS frameworks (inline styles or `<style>` block)\n- Auto-refresh every 10 seconds\n- Instance selector (paper/live) at the top\n\n## API Endpoints Available\n\nAll endpoints accept `?instance=paper` or `?instance=live` query param.\n\n1. `GET /api/status` → `{balance, equity, unrealized_pnl, open_positions, currency, source}`\n2. `GET /api/trades?limit=50` → `[{id, instrument, direction, units, price, stop_loss, take_profit, confidence, trade_id, timestamp, reason}]`\n3. `GET /api/pnl` → `{total_trades, instruments: {name: {trades, last_direction, last_price}}}`\n4. `GET /api/snapshots` → `[{timestamp, balance, equity, unrealized_pnl, open_positions, cycle}]` (chronological)\n5. `GET /api/signals` → `[{instrument, direction, confidence, sentiment, rsi_14, macd, adx}]` (sorted by confidence)\n6. `GET /api/sentiment` → `{instrument_name: score}` (scores -1.0 to 1.0)\n7. `GET /api/bot-log?limit=10` → `[{timestamp, cycle, summary: {instruments_scored, tradeable, top_signals, sentiment, model_accuracy}}]`\n8. `GET /api/instances` → `{paper: {name, running, generation, last_error}, live: {...}}`\n9. `POST /api/instances/<name>/start` → `{ok, instance}`\n10. `POST /api/instances/<name>/stop` → `{ok, instance}`\n11. `GET /api/engine-status` → `{running, cycle_count, instruments_warmed, model_accuracy, training_samples, pending_outcomes, halted, halt_reason}`\n12. `GET /api/settings` → `{granularity, min_confidence, risk_per_trade, stop_loss_atr_mult, take_profit_atr_mult, max_positions, daily_loss_limit, max_drawdown, cycle_seconds}`\n13. `POST /api/settings` → body: JSON object with key/value pairs to update\n\n## Dashboard Sections (top to bottom)\n\n### Header Bar\n- Title: \"Stockio\" with version badge\n- Instance toggle buttons: Paper | Live (highlight active)\n- Start/Stop button (context-aware based on running state)\n- Status indicator (running/stopped/halted with colored dot)\n\n### Portfolio Cards (row of 4 cards)\n- Balance (with currency)\n- Equity\n- Unrealized P&L (green if positive, red if negative)\n- Open Positions count\n\n### P&L Chart\n- Line chart (Chart.js) showing equity over time from snapshots\n- X-axis: timestamps, Y-axis: equity value\n- Subtle grid lines\n\n### Signals Panel\n- Table: Instrument | Direction | Confidence | Sentiment | RSI | MACD | ADX\n- Direction colored: BUY=green, SELL=red, HOLD=gray\n- Confidence as percentage\n- Sentiment colored: positive=green, negative=red\n\n### Trade History Panel\n- Table: Time | Instrument | Direction | Units | Price | SL | TP | Confidence | Trade ID\n- Direction colored\n- Most recent first\n- Scrollable, max height\n\n### Bot Thinking Log\n- Shows recent cycle summaries\n- Each entry: cycle number, instruments scored, signals generated, model accuracy\n- Collapsible entries\n\n### Engine Status Footer\n- Cycle count, model accuracy, training samples, pending outcomes\n- Circuit breaker status (halted warning if applicable)\n- Memory-compact single row\n\n### Settings Modal\n- Triggered by gear icon in header\n- Fields for: min_confidence, risk_per_trade, stop_loss_atr_mult, take_profit_atr_mult, max_positions, daily_loss_limit, max_drawdown, cycle_seconds\n- Save button that POSTs to /api/settings\n\n## Styling Notes\n- Background: #0f0f23 (dark navy)\n- Cards: #1a1a3e with subtle border\n- Text: #e0e0e0\n- Accent: #4fc3f7 (light blue)\n- BUY/positive: #4caf50\n- SELL/negative: #ef5350\n- HOLD: #9e9e9e\n- Font: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif\n- Monospace for numbers: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace\n\n## Important\n- Keep it under 1500 lines\n- Use vanilla JS (no frameworks)\n- All fetch calls should include `?instance=` + active instance\n- Handle errors gracefully (show \"No data\" instead of crashing)\n- The file should be a complete, self-contained HTML file with embedded CSS and JS\n\nWrite this file to `d:\\Nextcloud\\Projects\\Stockio\\src\\stockio\\templates\\dashboard.html`."},"uuid":"df72a708-5a63-43ec-9072-22aecec1e6ae","timestamp":"2026-04-08T23:34:16.760Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"D:\\Nextcloud\\Projects\\Stockio","sessionId":"daebbe58-d788-43b1-9532-396a80830200","version":"2.1.90","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"wild-juggling-clarke"}
